    <description><![CDATA[From Sweeny, turn on CR 316 for 4.2 miles, turn right on CR 318 for 1.5 miles<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 9302 CR 318, Brazoria]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-95.632214,28.93043,0</coordinates></Point>
